"Main_Content":
"來源: ClutchPoints
網址: https://tinyurl.com/yy2rlug8

NBA’s L2M report reveals Stephen Curry should have been called for travel
before pass to Shaun Livingston
聯盟裁判報告: Stephen Curry在傳給Shaun Livingston前就應該要被吹走步的

The NBA’s Last Two Minute Report released on Monday reveals that Golden
State Warriors star point guard Stephen Curry should have been called for a
travel before his pass to Shaun Livingston in the final seconds of Game 2 of
the NBA Finals on Sunday.
星期一聯盟公布了最後兩分鐘的裁判報告，在星期天Game 2比賽最後那個關鍵球，Stephen
Curry傳球給Shaun Livingston前就應該要被吹走步的。

影片支援: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4STZXTKoV6U
Curry’s pass to Livingston was almost intercepted by Raptors superstar
forward Kawhi Leonard
"Time":
but Livingston was somehow able to catch it while
Leonard was draped all over him.
Curry傳給Livingston的那球差一點就被暴龍明星Kawhi Leonard給抄走，不過Livingston
想辦法在Leonard撲到前把球接走。

Livingston then kicked it out to Warriors swingman Andre Iguodala
"Max_Word_Indicator":
who hit
the game-clinching 3-pointer to end the game. The Warriors wound up winning
Game 2 by a final score of 109-104.
Livingston隨後傳給勇士搖擺人Andre Iguodala，投進了那關鍵三分球鎖定了比賽。勇士
最後以109-104拿下Game 2。

Raptors fans were already upset with how the officials called Game 2
column6:
so this
new set of news isn’t going to sit well in Toronto.
暴龍粉已經對Game 2的裁判吹哨狀況很不爽了，這份報告出爐想必多倫多暴龍粉會更不開
心。

Refs will never be perfect
column7:
which is why a lot of people around the league don
’t even like the Last Two Minute Report to begin with. The series between
the Raptors and Warriors is now tied at 1-1
column8:
with Games 3 and 4 set to be
played in Oakland at Oracle Arena. Let’s see how the refs do in those games.
裁判永遠不會完美的，所以這也是一堆人都不喜歡這最後兩分鐘裁判報告的原因。這系列
戰目前兩隊戰成平手，Game 3跟Game 4會在甲骨文球場，所以就來看裁判接下來會怎麼吹
哨了。

If the travel was called
column9:
the Raptors would have gotten the ball back with
roughly 13 seconds remaining in regulation and the game score at 106-104.
如果那個哨有吹，暴龍就還會有13秒的機會進攻，比數那時是106-104。
--
"
